<Layout title="LG Washer Repair Los Angeles | $280–400 | Same Day" description="Same-day LG washer repair in Los Angeles, Orange County and Ventura County. Drain, fill, spin and error-code faults fixed. Most repairs $280–400. Call (323) 990-7550.">
  <div class="container" style="padding: 3rem 1.5rem; max-width: 820px;">
    <h1>LG Washer Repair in Los Angeles</h1>
    <p>We fix LG washing machines across Los Angeles, Orange County, and Ventura County — same-day in most cases, with most repairs landing at $280–400 including parts and labor. Drain faults, fill problems, error codes, no-spin, leaks: our techs diagnose on-site and quote a fixed number before any work, and the $65 diagnostic is waived when you approve the repair. Call (323) 990-7550.</p>

    <h2>LG Washer Error Codes</h2>
    <p>We diagnose and fix all LG washer error codes — tap your code for the cause, the DIY checks, and what a repair costs:</p>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(230px,1fr));gap:10px;margin:16px 0 8px;">
      <a href="/washer/error-codes/lg-washer-oe-error/" style="display:block;padding:12px 14px;background:#111b27;border:1px solid #1e2a3a;border-radius:8px;color:#c8d0dc;text-decoration:none;"><strong style="color:#1a6cf6;">OE</strong> – Won't drain</a>
      <a href="/washer/error-codes/lg-washer-ie-error/" style="display:block;padding:12px 14px;background:#111b27;border:1px solid #1e2a3a;border-radius:8px;color:#c8d0dc;text-decoration:none;"><strong style="color:#1a6cf6;">IE</strong> – Won't fill</a>
