      <a href="/washer/error-codes/lg-washer-le-error/" style="display:block;padding:12px 14px;background:#111b27;border:1px solid #1e2a3a;border-radius:8px;color:#c8d0dc;text-decoration:none;"><strong style="color:#1a6cf6;">LE</strong> – Motor locked</a>
